oard真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n重有邊打emoji打邊打中文又會黑了條選擇bar....."},{"pid":"b7df7f0c9c1c4e53cdf1f2774ef390d9640807b4","tid":324880,"uid":83060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T19:50:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>想問下邊個keyone最岩keyone用<br />\n利申用速成<br />\n想有emoji同關聯字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n中文輸入法我覺得 CedIME 最好用, 但無 emoji.</blockquote><br />\n完美夾到keyone?</blockquote><br />\n係咪alt enter轉中英文</blockquote><br />\n嗯...可以話算完美, 至少好過google輸入法個倉頡, CedIME 有關聯字, 有學習功能. 但中文標點得半形, 同埋會無咗 Password Keeper 嘅指紋 login 功能, 如果你用開 Password Keeper 就會明我講乜, 如果無用開唔駛理.<br />\n<br />\nCedIME 係 alt + space bar 轉中英"},{"pid":"47e1342fb7a320712194bb8870a62de9cde4b564","tid":324880,"uid":12222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T08:52:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>想問下邊個keyone最岩keyone用<br />\n利申用速成<br />\n想有emoji同關聯字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n中文輸入法我覺得 CedIME 最好用, 但無 emoji.</blockquote><br />\n完美夾到keyone?</blockquote><br />\n係咪alt enter轉中英文</blockquote><br />\n嗯...可以話算完美, 至少好過google輸入法個倉頡, CedIME 有關聯字, 有學習功能. 但中文標點得半形, 同埋會無咗 Password Keeper 嘅指紋 login 功能, 如果你用開 Password Keeper 就會明我講乜, 如果無用開唔駛理.<br />\n<br />\nCedIME 係 alt + space bar 轉中英</blockquote><br />\n不過無emoji又係on9 <br />\n用ig chat個d完全用唔到emoji"},{"pid":"f1aa77dde475e02fbb68e59a4ce1c2cf2b0903a4","tid":324880,"uid":40360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T14:17:01.000Z","msg":"唔好意思, 我想問下呢, 呢部嘢係咪都係要用專門比BB ge電話plan先可以收發email？"}]}